        <title>Support to the cohabitation of the population in the electoral period</title>
        <description>This project will be carried out for two needs:
1° need to work for the good cohabitation affecting electoral protagonists and the administrative municipal and provincial authorities for a good electoral success,
2° need, at the local level, to put together the various groups of the population.
The main activities involved in this operation are:
- Meetings with leaders of political parties on the electoral and on cohabitation issues   
- Sensibilisation of managers of election commissions, of the administrative and communal authorities and of leaders of Christian communities on the electoral issues.
- Training of managers of parish focal points on civic and democratic rights.</description>
