        <title>Education to peaceful cohabitatio between the local communities of the Diocese of BUBANZA </title>
        <description>This is to sensitize members of local communities to peaceful coexistence  by cohabitation education sessions . It will also raise awareness on the value and importance of the elections as being a popular choice and one of the models of democracy.
Activities to be conducted are the following :
1. Workshops training in peaceful cohabitation and peaceful resolution of conflicts 2. Training workshops in monitoring and electoral observation; 3. Training in monitoring and observation of human rights. 4. Two visits for the exchange of experience in 2 border dioceses (BUKAVU in DRC) and CYANGUGU in the RWANDA
</description>
